Description:
**UNDER OFFER / UNDER CONTRACT**
MAYFIELD ESTATE, CRANBOURNE EAST (124779270): **THIS PROPERTY IS LOCATED DIRECTLY OFF LINEHAM DRIVE** The problem with building is the time involved after you wait for the land to be released, then let the builder do their job, get the keys and move in, you could be looking at well over a year wasted. But, with this home in the flourishing Mayfield estate, not only has all this been done for you, but its also been fully landscaped and requires nothing more from you other than to move your furniture in, or to get a board up and lease out so why would you build?
Beautifully constructed by Porter Davis to a 7-star energy rating and finished by the owners with a keen eye for detail, this home has been occupied for less than six months and presents with display quality and style. Providing a low maintenance nature to suit a busy lifestyle, it features a gorgeous front facade and complementing gardens. Inside the timber look floors greet you upon entry and lead you to the open living/dining area where you will also find the galley style kitchen with stone benches, stainless appliances, soft close cabinetry and a semi-walk in pantry.
Theres also another living area upstairs plus 3 robed bedrooms, including the master with a walk in wardrobe and an impressive ensuite to match the family bathroom and additional downstairs powder room. A host of extras add to the comfort and appeal including double glazed windows throughout, ducted heating, evaporative cooling and LED downlights.
Outside theres a double remote garage with internal access and a landscaped courtyard with manicured lawns, a garden shed and an alfresco area with roof mounted speakers!
Within a short drive to freeway access and all amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne this sensational opportunity is only minutes away from the popular Clyde Primary School, Casey RACE Recreation & Aquatic Centre and Casey Indoor Sports Centre! With additional shopping precincts in Pasadena, Selandra Rise/Cascades on Clyde and The Hunt Club local amenities are always going to be close by, whilst the recently revamped Cranbourne Park Shopping Centre offers an abundance of cafes and restaurants! Don't forget the proposed Cranbourne East train station, or the existing ones situated right throughout the South East!
If you want your family to have easy access to the very best in entertainment, education and recreation then call before it's SELLING, SELLING ..... SOLD!
BOOK AN INSPECTION TODAY, IT MAY BE GONE TOMORROW! - *PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT OPEN FOR INSPECTIONS*!
At Ray White Cranbourne our price indications are based upon probable market value, the likely selling price and the vendor's expectations. You can view with confidence that vendors will sell within the range with favourable conditions.
Our floor plans are for representational purposes only and should be used as such. We accept no liability for the accuracy or details contained in our floor plans.

Description:
Looking for a BIG SHED???
CRANBOURNE EAST - (HUNT CLUB) - sitting on approx. 612sqm is this beautiful home, consisting of 4 large bedrooms, master with full ensuite and WIR.
The property has a natural flow in the layout which offers a fantastic formal lounge flowing into a large open plan family living area and dining area. All of this is overlooked by a modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances as well as plenty of cupboard and bench space to complete the picture.
On offer there are 2 large undercover outdoor areas, which are perfect for entertaining family and friends. As well as a good size backyard for the kids to play.
Other Extras in the property include, ducted heating & air conditioning, fully landscaped gardens back and front, and much much more.
The biggest highlight of this property is its ENORMOUS 5.5 x 12 metre shed, with more than enough space for 4-6 cars, boats, and bikes or any other toys you could wish for. In addition to that you also a huge driveway, another double garage under rood and enough outdoor space to park multiple other vehicles
This park front home is also located within a very short walking distance to the Cranbourne east school, child care centre, parks, wetlands and transport, and the hunt club shopping village.
All the hard work has been done for you which makes this property is a perfect place for a large family to grow. Do not want to miss out, call today for an inspection before it's gone.
Features include:
- 4 Bedrooms, Master with full ensuite & walk in robe.
- 2 separate Living Areas.
- Extras in the property include ducted heating & A/C & much more.
- Kitchen with plenty of cupboard and bench space & stainless steel appliances.
- A HUGE 5.5 x 12 meter shed, a double garage underroof + extra outdoor vehicle space.
- 2 separate undercover outdoor areas, overlooking a great backyard.

Description:
Unique 2.5 Year young Home on 650sqm Block with self contained granny flat
This magnificent barely 2.5 year young 3 or 4 bedroom brick veneer home is in the precinct
of the sought after Hunt Club area.This versatile property would suit a business person,
growing family, extended family or just to enjoy lifestyle.
It has a master bedroom with en-suite. All rooms have built in robes.The 9 ft ceilings give a
feeling of spaciousness.A great feature is the extra large garage with above average height
doors for higher vehicles.

**UNDER OFFER / UNDER CONTRACT**
LIVINGSTON ESTATE, CRANBOURNE EAST (124751186): **THIS PROPERTY IS LOCATED ADJACENT TO THE CORNER OF NELSON STREET & BOON WURRUNG STREET** Brand new and ready to move into and enjoy, this home is set deep within the blossoming Livingston estate and begs one simple question why bother building? Save the time, energy and stress and either settle into your first home or lease it out with ease in an area desperate for quality rentals!
Fronted by a thoroughly modern facade with rendered highlights you step through the solid timber door to find a well-planned home with a central hallway leading you to the open and tiled living/dining room. The stylish kitchen with moody dark cabinetry, stone benches and stainless appliances is a sure hit for the house chef!
There is accommodation for a growing family too with 4 robed bedrooms, including the master that has a walk through wardrobe and a full ensuite leaving the family bathroom for the remaining rooms. Not to mention the additional study/multipurpose zone upon entry!
Ducted heating is included to ease the freezing Melbourne winters whilst outside theres a double garage and a backyard that is a blank canvas ready for you to create a low maintenance entertaining space to use with family and friends.
Within a short drive to freeway access and all amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne this sensational opportunity is only minutes away from the popular Clyde Primary School, Casey RACE Recreation & Aquatic Centre and Casey Indoor Sports Centre! With additional shopping precincts in Pasadena, Selandra Rise/Cascades on Clyde and The Hunt Club local amenities are always going to be close by, whilst the recently revamped Cranbourne Park Shopping Centre offers an abundance of cafes and restaurants! Don't forget the proposed Cranbourne East train station, or the existing ones situated right throughout the South East!
If you want your family to have easy access to the very best in entertainment, education and recreation then call today before it's SELLING, SELLING ..... SOLD!

Description:
MASSIVE 660m2 IN CASCADES ON CLYDE!
Cranbourne East: Located in the picturesque Cascades on Clyde estate sits this astonishing four bedroom home situated on an impressive 660m2 block!
The generous sized master bedroom comes complete with full en-suite and walk in robes with dual vanities and extended shower space, while the three guest bedrooms come fitted with built in robes of their own, as an added bonus the fourth bedroom has access to the alfresco through a timber sliding door of its own.
The kitchen which comes complete with stainless steel appliances, 900mm range hood, 5 burner gas cook top, glass splash back, Caesar stone bench tops, ample amounts of bench space and overhead storage, not to mention a functional amount of pantry space, all overlooking the alfresco and huge central living zone.
There is also the convenient separate living area which can be used to accommodate the needs of any family, whether it be a childrens retreat, open study or extra living space, the opportunity is yours.
Added features include: internal access, evaporative cooling & ducted heating, neutral tones throughout, garden sheds, timber sliding doors and side access.
Step through your timber sliding doors to be greeted by your huge completely decked alfresco, not to mention the huge 660m2 block! This provides the perfect spot to entertain guests and family of all sizes while having more than enough backyard space for the kids to enjoy.
The additions dont stop there, as you drive along this quiet, nestled away street, youll recognize the enormous street appeal this home has to offer, with a completely landscaped front and rear yard, youll be able to appreciate the amount of effort that has gone into the making of this perfect family home.
Surrounded by top end properties and is within walking distance to picturesque wetlands, this home boasts convenience. Other estate features include Class- A recycled water ensuring lush gardens year round, over 14 hectares of parkland and public open space, public BBQ facilities, playgrounds and walking tracks.
Those who are business savvy will appreciate this Telstra smart community positioned within a short drive to all amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne. Minutes away from freeway access enroute to the Melbourne CBD, the popular Clyde Primary School, brand new child care centre, the recently constructed Casey Fields football ground/Casey Race aquatic centre and the Town Centre. Not to mention just seconds away from the newly developed Selanda rise and hunt Club village shopping centres.
Rare opportunities like these dont last long!

Description:
DREAMS DO COME TRUE
CRANBOURNE EAST: This little gem of a home is located in the much sought-after Livingstone Estate. Built by the award winners Porter Davis Homes, this home has it all and in abundance. On approach to this home you will be greeted by aura and elegance.
As you walk thru the doors of this double-storey home, you will be greeted by a grand entrance way which leads into the open plan kitchen, dining and family areas an entertainers delight with a self-contained powder room. The kitchen is equipped with quality stainless appliances, a dishwasher and plenty of storage space.
The bedrooms are located above and are planned very strategically to provide for peace and quiet after those long and tiring days. The master bedroom offers full en suite and large built-in robes. The other two bedroom are spacious and come with large built-in robes located close to the second shower and bath. Alongside the bath and shower is a rumpus room for the kids to enjoy and unwind.
This home is designed to let in plenty of natural light, is in a very safe location and is situated in a safe neighborhood.
Added internal and external features include:
-Built in 2015
-Under builders warranty
-Multiple living areas
-Rumpus room
-Air conditioner
-600 mm gas cook top
-600 mm oven
-Caesar stone bench tops
-Designer tap in the kitchen
-Dishwasher
-Ducted heating
-Three toilets including powder room
-Double garage
-Internal access
-Alfresco
*Local park and play ground are stones throw away from the house
*South Gippsland Highway is approximately three minutes drive away from the house
*Casey Race is approximately two minutes drive away from the house
*Casey Fields is approximately two minutes drive away from the house
*Cranbourne Shopping Centre is approximately five minutes drive away from the house
*St Peters College is approximately five minutes drive away from the house
*Casey Grammar School is approximately five minutes drive away from the house
*St Thomas Primary School is approximately six minuted drive away from the house

Description:
Big Blocks Are Beautiful
Sitting on a massive approx. 720 sqm block this family home is a great entertainer. Located in one of the most well know estate of Cranbourne, Hunt Club Estate has to offer numerous parks, shopping centre, wetlands, walking and bicycle paths, child care facilities, primary as well as secondary schools, public transport through the estate, high speed broadband and environmentally friendly designs are all part of the estate.
Features include:
- 4 large bedrooms, master with full ensuite & WIR
- 2 huge separate large living areas plus a rumpus room
- Kitchen with stainless steel appliances with heaps of cupboard & bench space
- Large pergola overlooking a massive backyard.
- Large double garage, with rear access roller door.
- Side access with a possibility of parking space for caravans, trailers, cars or boats
Other features: downlights, large garden ahed, gas ducted heating and dishwasher
Furthermore with short distance walk to The Casey Complex, Casey Grammar School, Marnebek School, Cranbourne Library and Leisure centre, this location is a perfect spot of the life time. Don't miss this opportunity contact Yogi Patel - 0451 719 161 to arrange a private appointment.
Photo Id require for all inspections.

Description:
THE COMPLETE PACKAGE
CRANBOURNE EAST: With extraordinary attention to detail, no expense has been spared in the construction of this one of a kind family home. Ideally suited to both first timers and down sizers, this functional floor plan would also suit those who are looking to invest.
This magnificent property is situated in an established street location within the prestigious Parks Edge Estate. It is simply a case of moving in, unpacking and enjoying a luxurious lifestyle.
The master bedroom offers a full en suite with walk in robe. There is plenty of space in the master bedroom for you to have your own dressing table or TV stand. All the other bedrooms have double door built in robes and they are located at a distance from the master bed room. The spacious and separate bathroom is set up close to the other bedrooms.
Anyone who enjoys an open plan structure will surely fall in love with the makeup of the kitchen, study area, open plan living and the outdoor access to the alfresco area with decking. This gem of a house offers fully secure and landscaped gardens as well.
Summary of internal and external features include:
- Built in 2013
- Approx. 400sqm land
- Study area with built in desk
- Porcelain tiles
- High ceiling
- Glass Splash Back
- Caesar stone bench top in Kitchen
- 900 mm stainless steel oven
- 900 mm cook top
- Large fridge space
- Microwave cavity
- Built in Pantry
- Dishwasher
- Overhead cupboards in the kitchen
- Stainless steel range hood
- Ducted heating
- Solar power electricity
- Remote controlled double lock up garage
- Internal access
- Overhead cupboards in the laundry
- Sliding doors in to Alfresco
- Alfresco and Decking area
- Fully landscaped garden
- Fully secure backyard
* The location of this quality home is second to none with all the major amenities on your door step. Your family can enjoy the open space for many years to come.
This property is situated within close proximity to Cranbourne East Primary and Cranbourne East Secondary College, as well as Cranbourne Secondary College and is surrounded by multiple Shopping Centres. Also located nearby, is the newly constructed Casey Fields football ground, Casey Race Recreation & Aquatic Centre and Casey Library.
BOOK AN INSPECTION TODAY, IT MAY BE GONE TOMORROW! - *PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT OPEN FOR INSPECTIONS*
